title: Storm Doris: Dashcam captures falling tree near miss - BBC News
text:
Media playback is unsupported on your device Storm Doris: Dashcam captures falling tree near miss 23 February 2017 Last updated at 17:25 GMT 
Dashcam footage from driving instructor Paul Smith shows a narrow escape from a falling tree in Spalding. 
Storm Doris has been bringing winds of up to 94mph, along with snow and rain to the UK. Read more
